#  ALLEGRO4_INCLUDE_DIRS
#  ALLEGRO4_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use ALLEGRO4.
#  ALLEGRO4_LIBRARY_DIRS, the location of the libraries
#  ALLEGRO4_FOUND, If false, do not try to use ALLEGRO4
